mmdvm Licensing
===============

This crate is distributed under the GNU General Public License, version 2
or (at your option) any later version (GPL-2.0-or-later). This matches the
workspace-wide license choice for the kenwood project.

mmdvm is a tokio async shell for the MMDVM ham-radio digital voice modem
protocol. It builds on the sans-io mmdvm-core crate and implements the
event-loop / queue / handle orchestration described in the reference C++
implementation MMDVMHost (https://github.com/g4klx/MMDVMHost), which is
distributed under GPL-2.0-or-later for the files that inform this crate's
derivation.

